    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can use your Channel Divinity to rebuke those who use violence. Immediately after a creature within 30 feet of you deals damage in a turn to creatures other than you, you can use your reaction to force the damage dealing creature to make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, they takes radiant damage equal to the damage it just dealt on the turn. On a successful save, it takes half as much damage.</p>",
